divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS OUTSIDE LOOKING AT THE STARS , THEIR WAS BROKEN CLOUD COVER AT THE TIME,WHEN I SAW WHITE LIGHT COMEING FROM THE NORTH AT VERY HIGH SPEED.I ALSO SAW IT WAS UNDER THE CLOUDS.IT WAS MOVEING FROM,NORTH , TO SOUTH.IT SEEMED TO BE CHANGING SPEEDS, SLOWING DOWN.AND SPEEDING UP.IT THEN MADE A QUICK CIRCLE, THEN , MOVED SOUTH AT VERY HIGH SPEED.IWAS IN THE YARD OF MY APARTMENT.I NOTICED THE OBJECT BECAUSE OF IT SPEED.I THOUGHT IT WAS A PLANE. I WAS THINKING WHAT IS THIS.
